Popular Television host, Ebuka Obi-Uchendu’s wife, Cynthia Obi-Uchendu took to her Instagram page recently to gush over her dotting husband. The fashion entrepreneur shared a short clip of her spouse applying relaxer on her hair while she sat on a chair, blushing and filming the event. The talk show host apparently could make for a good hairstylist a discipline he can potentially add to his portfolio. Cynthia said since her hubby has discovered a new talent, she’ll then put him to work. She wrote, FEC approves 1.2bn Euros loan for agric mechanization “He has discovered another talent. Putting him to work”.